{
  "stem": "5644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This pipe is very important to know about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A, a, a sewer pipe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we couldn't go over, because we'll be too close to the--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surface.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got to go under.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So made a step down for the pipe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's very important to know about the pipe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll tell you in a minute why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'd been sent out by the top two boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Across the street was only about five, six houses where one side could see a street about five kilometers, and on another side, about five kilometers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we are standing on both sides.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got a gun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got a machine gun, and we got a revolver.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is one guard on one side, and another one on another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't said which way they will come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This street or that street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all security.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, boys, if you will see him-- they described them quite well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there wasn't a big traffic, because near a wall-- because in the middle of the street of Muranowska between 7 and between 6 was a wall.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto wall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there, if the Poles even come home, they rushed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want to be near the wall, because something can happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, that you could see immediately who is who.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if you will see the two people, one will be Jewish-looking-- that's Karski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one would be Polish-looking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Big mustaches, big mustaches, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jewish fellow didn't look exactly like him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they told, we told, to dress themselves as Jewish as you can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they're Christian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they went to the-- they came through my side.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
